rows.label: qst200818_0010
rows.name:
Onee-chan, thank you for protecting
everyone and the great tree.

rows.label: qst200818_0020
rows.name:
It wasn't just my power. It
was thanks to everyone.

rows.label: qst200818_0030
rows.name:
I think we were able to protect this
tree because everyone worked hard...

rows.label: qst200818_0040
rows.name:
There are people who don't cherish
nature, but there are also many who do.

rows.label: qst200818_0050
rows.name: That's right. I love this tree.

rows.label: qst200818_0060
rows.name:
It's the town's treasure, so
we have to take care of it.

rows.label: qst200818_0070
rows.name:
I'm glad... Please
continue to cherish it.

rows.label: qst200818_0090
rows.name:
Also... I'd rather you not call me
Onee-chan. Because I'm an Onii-chan.
